126
00:06:35,779 --> 00:06:37,997
I warned them about the storm.

127
00:06:39,533 --> 00:06:41,917
They don't care.

128
00:06:41,952 --> 00:06:44,370
They won't even let me in the command tent.

129
00:06:49,009 --> 00:06:50,876
But they'll let you in, right?

130
00:06:52,379 --> 00:06:53,796
What do I tell them?

131
00:06:57,184 --> 00:06:59,986
Whoa! Charlie! Charlie!

132
00:07:00,020 --> 00:07:02,271
Fritz! You're here.

133
00:07:02,306 --> 00:07:03,472
Yeah.

134
00:07:03,523 --> 00:07:06,142
I'm glad. Grab a radio.

135
00:07:06,193 --> 00:07:08,394
Make sure the circuit cables
don't short out in the rain.

136
00:07:08,396 --> 00:07:09,895
Whoa, whoa, we're supposed to meet

137
00:07:09,897 --> 00:07:11,897
