before we pull the trigger.

138
00:07:11,899 --> 00:07:15,151
Visibility over 45 miles,
humidity below 85%...

139
00:07:15,202 --> 00:07:16,786
Yeah, I read the report.

140
00:07:16,820 --> 00:07:19,572
But you got to talk to the
Colonel, delay the test.

141
00:07:19,574 --> 00:07:22,992
The Colonel and I aren't
on the best of terms.

142
00:07:23,043 --> 00:07:25,578
Ready to go.

143
