- Yes.
- To babysit Shiva, the god of death,

168
00:08:53,133 --> 00:08:54,834
in the middle of an electrical storm.

169
00:08:54,868 --> 00:08:57,253
Well, maybe the Japs can
spare a kamikaze pilot.

170
00:08:57,304 --> 00:08:59,805
- I want one guy.
- I, I don't have a man to spare.

171
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:02,174
