- What is it that you want?

172
00:09:02,176 --> 00:09:04,894
This is a war. I don't
care about one guy!

173
00:09:04,928 --> 00:09:08,063
- Right.
- I'll do it.

174
00:09:08,098 --> 00:09:09,648
No way.

175
00:09:09,683 --> 00:09:10,983
If the Colonel wants to
double-check the detonators,

176
00:09:11,017 --> 00:09:12,518
