177
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:14,153
We're concerned about the
possibility of sabotage.

178
00:09:14,187 --> 00:09:15,905
It's just a precaution.

179
00:09:15,939 --> 00:09:18,324
No wife, no kids. I'll do it.

180
00:09:18,358 --> 00:09:21,360
- I'll do it.
- No, you're more valuable on the ground.

181
00:09:21,362 --> 00:09:24,246
Jim, you don't have to.

182
00:09:24,281 --> 00:09:25,581
It's okay.

183
00:09:25,615 --> 00:09:27,700
It should be someone you trust.

184
00:09:43,049 --> 00:09:45,968
Hey! Hey, you!

185
00:09:48,054 --> 00:09:50,523
Boy Wonder said to give you this.

186
00:09:53,059 --> 00:09:54,059
Start the clock.

187
00:09:56,029 --> 00:09:58,647
Zero minus 150 minutes.

188
00:09:58,698 --> 00:10:00,149
Begin the evacuation...

189
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,117
By 0430 hours,

190
00:10:02,152 --> 00:10:03,953
