208
00:12:35,700 --> 00:12:37,785
You and Frank built this bomb.

209
00:12:37,787 --> 00:12:40,254
I have no doubts about
how destructive it will be.

210
00:12:40,288 --> 00:12:43,090
Your signature's all over
that mess of wires, too.

